        "Description": "Welcome to Whittleton Creek, 47!\r\rYour target are builders who have been stealing expensive building materials for a long time and using them for their own purposes. Our client - a large and influential construction company, does not want to suffer any more looses and wants to put an end to it. You have to eliminate all 5 targets by available means without attracting unnecessary attention. As soon as you complete the mission, leave the area in a construction van.\r\rGood hunting, 47!",
